4.1.3.25unsigned int libify ( ctx_t  ctx )

Main routine LOAD OPERATIONS

Load each section of binary using bfd

Print BFD sections

Read .text segment boundaries

Open target binary

Read sections from disk

Read symtab + strtab : BFD doesnt do this

Read symbols

Add extra symbols

Parse relocations

Fix section indexes in symtab

PROCESSING

Copy each section content in output le

Relocation stripping

Create Program Headers

FINAL WRITE OPERATIONS

Write strtab and symtab

Add section headers to output le

Add segment headers to output le

4.9.3.26int libcall ( lua_State  L )
